sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application<br/>Inference Workload
    participant TrainJob as Training Job<br/>Model Training
    participant FeastCLI as Feast CLI/SDK<br/>Feature Engineer
    participant OnlineFS as Online Feature Server<br/>6566/6567 TCP<br/>gRPC/HTTP
    participant OfflineFS as Offline Feature Server<br/>8815/8816 TCP<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Registry as Registry Server<br/>6570/6571 TCP gRPC<br/>6572/6573 TCP REST
    participant Redis as Redis/PostgreSQL<br/>Online Store
    participant S3 as S3/Object Storage<br/>Offline Store
    participant CronJob as CronJob<br/>Materialization

    Note over MLApp,S3: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval (Real-time Inference)
    MLApp->>OnlineFS: POST /get-online-features<br/>Auth: Bearer/mTLS<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    OnlineFS->>Registry: Get feature metadata<br/>gRPC 6570/6571<br/>Auth: Bearer/mTLS
    Registry-->>OnlineFS: Feature schema
    OnlineFS->>Redis: Read features<br/>6379/5432 TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    Redis-->>OnlineFS: Feature values
    OnlineFS-->>MLApp: Feature response<br/>gRPC/HTTP

    Note over TrainJob,S3: Flow 2: Historical Feature Retrieval (Training)
    TrainJob->>OfflineFS: POST /get-historical-features<br/>Auth: Bearer/mTLS<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    OfflineFS->>Registry: Get feature metadata<br/>gRPC 6570/6571<br/>Auth: Bearer/mTLS
    Registry-->>OfflineFS: Feature schema
    OfflineFS->>S3: Read historical data<br/>443 TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS IAM Auth
    S3-->>OfflineFS: Historical features
    OfflineFS-->>TrainJob: Training dataset<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over CronJob,Redis: Flow 3: Feature Materialization (Offline to Online)
    CronJob->>OnlineFS: POST /materialize<br/>Auth: Bearer/mTLS<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    OnlineFS->>OfflineFS: Fetch offline features<br/>8815/8816 TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    OfflineFS-->>OnlineFS: Feature data
    OnlineFS->>Redis: Write to online store<br/>6379/5432 TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    Redis-->>OnlineFS: Confirmation
    OnlineFS-->>CronJob: Materialization complete

    Note over FeastCLI,S3: Flow 4: Feature Registry Management
    FeastCLI->>Registry: ApplyFeatureView<br/>gRPC 6570/6571<br/>Auth: Bearer/mTLS
    Registry->>S3: Store metadata<br/>443 TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS IAM (if S3 backend)
    S3-->>Registry: Confirmation
    Registry-->>FeastCLI: Success response
